("en","ai-everyday","You want to use ChatGPT to create a weekly meal plan for your family. Some members have severe food allergies. How do you approach this?","The more specific your prompts, the safer and more useful the AI output will be for everyone.",O(("Include all allergies, dietary preferences, and portion sizes in your initial prompt for accurate meal results.","Perfect! Detailed context ensures the AI generates safe and well-tailored meal plans."),("Ask for a generic meal plan and manually check each recipe afterwards for potential allergen ingredients.","Works but risky — you might overlook hidden allergens in complex recipes and ingredients."),("Trust the AI to automatically detect and avoid allergens based on your previous conversation history data.","Dangerous! AI does not remember your medical data unless you explicitly provide it each time.")),1),
("en","ai-everyday","You are planning a vacation to Italy and use an AI assistant for recommendations. It suggests a hotel that looks perfect. How do you proceed?","AI travel recommendations are starting points — always verify availability and current reviews independently.",O(("Use the AI suggestion as a starting point, then verify ratings on Booking.com and check recent reviews.","Smart approach! Cross-referencing AI suggestions with current reviews ensures quality and accuracy."),("Ignore the AI completely and spend hours manually searching through dozens of travel booking websites.","Possible but inefficient — AI suggestions can significantly speed up your initial research process."),("Book the hotel immediately based solely on the AI recommendation to secure the room before others.","Risky! AI data may be outdated — the hotel could be closed, renovated, or poorly managed now.")),1),
("en","ai-everyday","Your friend asks you to enhance their portrait photo using an AI editing app for their social media profile. What do you consider?","AI photo editing is powerful but transparency about modifications preserves trust and authenticity.",O(("Make subtle enhancements like lighting and color, and let your friend know which AI tools were used.","Perfect! Subtle improvements plus transparency is the responsible approach to AI photo editing."),("Refuse to use AI tools entirely and suggest they hire a professional photographer for a new session.","Valid option but overkill — AI tools can achieve great results for casual social media photos."),("Use AI to dramatically change their appearance — slimmer face, perfect skin — as a fun surprise.","Problematic! Significant alterations without consent can damage self-image and personal trust.")),2),
("en","ai-everyday","You are using an AI shopping assistant to find deals on electronics. It recommends a laptop from an unknown brand at half price. What do you do?","AI can find great deals, but verifying seller reputation and product quality remains your responsibility.",O(("Research the brand independently, read verified customer reviews, and check the return policy before buying.","Excellent! Due diligence on AI recommendations protects you from scams and poor quality products."),("Ignore the recommendation entirely and only buy from the most expensive well-known brand available online.","Safe but costly — some lesser-known brands genuinely offer good value with proper prior research."),("Buy it immediately since the AI found the best deal and must have compared all available options already.","Dangerous! AI may recommend unknown brands without verifying legitimacy or actual product quality.")),1),
("en","ai-everyday","You want to use AI to help redecorate your living room. You upload a photo and receive an impressive design suggestion. What is next?","AI designs inspire creativity, but real-world constraints like measurements and budget need human verification.",O(("Use the design as inspiration, measure your room carefully, and create a realistic budget before buying.","Smart! AI designs are great starting points but need real-world validation before any purchases."),("Save the design but never act on it because AI-generated interior designs are probably not practical.","Too dismissive! Many AI design suggestions are surprisingly practical with just minor adjustments."),("Order all suggested furniture immediately online to transform your room exactly as the AI design shows.","Risky! Without measuring first, furniture may not fit and returns are expensive and wasteful.")),2),
("en","ai-everyday","Your child wants to use an AI chatbot to help write a school essay about their summer vacation. How do you guide them through this?","AI is a creative tool for children too — guidance ensures they learn while using technology responsibly.",O(("Encourage them to use AI for brainstorming ideas, then write the essay in their own words and voice.","Perfect! Using AI for inspiration while maintaining authentic voice teaches responsible AI use."),("Forbid any AI use completely and insist they write everything from scratch using only printed resources.","Overly restrictive — teaching responsible AI use prepares children better for the modern future."),("Let them submit the AI-generated text directly as their own work without any personal modifications.","Wrong! Submitting AI text as own work is dishonest and undermines the learning objective entirely.")),1),
("en","ai-everyday","You use an AI voice assistant while driving to dictate text messages. The assistant frequently misinterprets words and names. How do you handle it?","Voice assistants work best with clear articulation — always review messages before sending them out.",O(("Speak clearly, use simple sentences, and always review the transcribed message before sending it out.","Correct! Clear speech and review prevent embarrassing autocorrect failures consistently each time."),("Stop using voice features entirely and type all messages manually while keeping one hand on the wheel.","Dangerous! Manual typing while driving is far riskier than using voice with proper review."),("Continue dictating naturally and send messages without checking because the AI is usually accurate enough.","Risky! Misinterpreted words can cause serious misunderstandings in professional and personal contexts.")),2),
("en","ai-everyday","You are using an AI fitness app that creates personalized workout plans. After a week, you experience persistent knee pain. What do you do?","AI fitness plans cannot replace medical advice — always listen to your body and consult professionals.",O(("Stop the workout immediately, see a doctor, and then adjust the AI settings based on medical advice.","Correct! Health always comes first — AI plans need human medical oversight when issues arise."),("Delete the app permanently and give up on structured training because AI fitness plans clearly fail.","Overreaction — after medical clearance, a properly adjusted AI plan can still be very helpful."),("Push through the pain because the AI algorithm must have calculated the optimal training intensity level.","Dangerous! AI cannot feel your pain or know your body — ignoring pain risks serious injury.")),2),
