("en","ai-everyday","You are abroad and use an AI translation app to communicate with a local doctor about a health concern. How do you use the app?","For medical conversations, AI translation is a helpful aid but should be supplemented with professional help.",O(("Use the app as a communication aid and also request a professional interpreter for medical accuracy.","Correct! Medical conversations require professional accuracy that AI alone simply cannot guarantee."),("Skip the app entirely and attempt to communicate through gestures and basic words without any tools.","Brave but impractical — the app can help significantly even if it is not perfectly accurate always."),("Rely entirely on the AI translation app to convey your symptoms and understand the diagnosis completely.","Dangerous! Translation errors in medical contexts can lead to misdiagnosis or wrong treatment.")),3),
